  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The primary efficacy assessment is the change from baseline in International Prostate Symptom Score (IPSS) total score at the end-of-study (EOS) visit.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Efficacy: changes from baseline in IPSS total score by visit;·IPSS irritative and obstructive subscores,·urinary peak flow rate and residual urine volume at EOS and by visit.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
