  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  suffering from LUTS related to BPH for at least 6 months;

          -  having an IPSS &gt;13;

          -  having a urinary peak flow rate 5.0 to 12.0 mL/s for a voided volume of at least 150
             mL;

          -  having a residual urine volume &lt; or = 200 mL.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
